Using window like snipping tool in Ubuntu 16.04

Press shift + printscr --> a mouse pointer select is highlighted.
Select the screen and copy it on the clipboard
===================================================================

Merging multiple PDF files commandline using gs

gs -dNOPAUSE -sDEVICE=pdfwrite -sOUTPUTFILE=merged_file.pdf -dBATCH first.pdf second.pdf 
